            <td colspan="1">$n - Number of part/section of a work (R) <br>$p - Name of part/section of a work (R) <br>$x - International Standard Serial Number (NR) <br>$6 - Linkage (NR) <br>$8 - Field link and sequence number (R) <br></td>
